 on acoustics, speech and signal processing (ICASSP) , pp. 5206–5210 . Cited by: §4.1 . [20] C. Pavlovic (2018) SII—speech intelligibility index standard: ansi s3. 5 1997 . the Journal of the Acoustical Society of America 143 ( 3_Supplement ), pp. 1906–1906 . Cited by: §2.3 . [21] K. J. Piczak (2015) ESC: dataset for environmental", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false, "persistedOutputPath": "/inspire/qb-ilm/project/video-generation/chenxie-25019/hyr/iHateTheWorld555.github.io/.claude-review/projects/-inspire-qb-ilm-project-video-generation-chenxie-25019-hyr-iHateTheWorld555-github-io/074a0690-4ec6-4d3a-bcf1-9500ad4e2daf/tool-results/btbvrpx0c.txt", "persistedOutputSize": 32632}}
